## Welcome to Mycelial Communications
We Provides analysis, design and systems integration consulting services for organizations that are implementing secure communication strategies.  

Our complete solutions have proven reliability, and set the standard for todays high security voice and video communication.  We pride ourselves in our flexibility and agile development procedures, customizing our software to fit your needs.

## We want to work with you on
* Secure communication strategies
* High performance telephony systems
* Public telephony networks
* Cellular encryption systems

## Please contact us for more information
Toll free: 888-888-88888

By Email: support@mycelialcomm.net
